data.description: Immaculate home in Westcreek, one of the largest floor plans with a grand wooden staircase and second living area upon entry.  Brick fire place faces open kitchen dining with perfect view of your amazing back yard with covered patio to enjoy quite mornings or family gatherings. The entire home has been newly painted, downstairs floors combined ceramic and wood like plank tile, brand new carpet on second floor.  Master bath has upgraded ceramic glazed subway tile on a beautiful garden tub and glass shower. New HVAC & Dishwasher as of 07/2020!  Lots of mature trees & privacy fence for plenty of shade privacy. Includes storage shed. Garage has built in storage units that stay with new homeowner. Ready to move in!
